quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  93,1,Ka khalalelo ea khanya ea mats`a
  93,2,Le ka bosiu nakong eo bo es’ong ho se ts’ekhe
  93,3,Hore Mong`a hau ha A es’o u lahle kherehloa le hona ho u hloea
  93,4,Bophelo Bo-tlang bo tla ba molemo ho uena ho feta ba lefats’e
  93,5,Mong`a hau U tla u neha tsohle tse molemo hore u tle u khotsofale
  93,6,"Na ha se eena ea u fumaneng u le khutsana, a u lopolla"
  93,7,"Na ha se Eena Ea u fumaneng u ntse u phaqola, A u tataisa"
  93,8,"Na ha se Eena Ea u fumaneng u hloka letho, A u ruisa"
  93,9,"Ka lebaka leo, u se hatelle khutsana"
  93,10,Le hona ho leleka mokopi
  93,11,U phatlalatse nala ea Mong`a hau